<main class="md:mx-28">
  <div class="flex flex-col">
    <div class="text-center text-4xl font-oswald tracking-wider text-moss py-2 pt-20 md:pt-24">Who are we? </div>
      <div class="text-xl text-moss font-barlow text-center mx-4 flex py-2 justify-between md:text-2xl md:py-4">Green is now is passionate about informing and educating people about the importance of introducing eco-friendly habits. We are commited to long-term sustainibility and as a team, we spent time researching a way to calculate your carbon emissions saved. We hope this website provides you with insightful information as well as inspires you to reduce your carbon footprint. </div>
        <div class="text-center p-2"> <i class="fab fa-pagelines text-moss text-3xl"></i> </div>

        </div>

    </div>
      <div class="text-center text-4xl font-oswald tracking-wider text-moss py-2">References <i class="fas fa-books"></i></div>
        <div class="text-xl text-moss font-barlow text-center mx-4 py-2 md:text-2xl md:py-4">Our main source is from "The Carbon Footprint of Everything" by Mike Berners-Lee. We have also included a list of all the websites that helped inform us about our daily carbon emissions.</div>

          <div class="text-l font-barlow text-moss pt-2 flex flex-col text-left mx-4 md:text-xl">
            <% i = 0 %>
            <% @references.each do |reference| %>
            <div class="py-2"><%= i += 1 %> . <%= reference.name %></div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div  class='flex justify-center pt-2 object-cover'> <%= image_tag 'booksref.JPG', style: "width: 25px; height: 25px;" %></div>
        <div class="bg-lightsand" style="height: 20px"></div>
</main>
